 r‚ÜêUpload(author name source avatar);lines;tmpns;ns;overwritten;dir;path;meta;ens
‚çù Upload a user bot: validate, save to disk, install into runtime
 ‚éïIO‚Üê0
 ‚çù Reject if name matches a built-in
 :If 0‚â†##.Rhobots.‚éïNC‚äÇname
     ‚éïSIGNAL‚äÇ('EN' 11)('Message'('Name conflicts with built-in bot: ',name))
 :EndIf
 ‚çù Validate source by fixing into a temp namespace
 ‚çù NOTE: if source is invalid, 2 ‚éïFIX prints "error AC0040: could not fix function"
 ‚çù to the session before signalling DOMAIN ERROR. This output cannot be suppressed
 ‚çù by :Trap ‚Äî it is diagnostic output from the interpreter, not an error signal.
 ‚çù It is harmless noise. See AC0040 repo for details.
 lines‚Üê(‚éïUCS 10)(‚â†‚äÜ‚ä¢)source
 tmpns‚Üê‚éïNS''
 :Trap 0
     2 tmpns.‚éïFIX lines
 :Else
     ‚éïSIGNAL‚äÇ('EN' 11)('Message'('Source failed to fix: ',‚éïDMX.Message))
 :EndTrap
 ‚çù Check Init and Tick exist with correct valence
 ns‚Üêtmpns‚çéname
 :If 3‚â†ns.‚éïNC'Init'
     ‚éïSIGNAL‚äÇ('EN' 11)('Message' 'Bot must define Init as a function')
 :EndIf
 :If 3‚â†ns.‚éïNC'Tick'
     ‚éïSIGNAL‚äÇ('EN' 11)('Message' 'Bot must define Tick as a function')
 :EndIf
 ‚çù Check overwrite
 path‚Üê##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author,'/',name,'.apln'
 overwritten‚Üê‚éïNEXISTS path
 ‚çù Ensure author dir exists and write files
 dir‚Üê##.Cfg.USER_BOTS_PATH,'/',author
 3 ‚éïMKDIR dir
 (‚äÇsource)‚éïNPUT path 1
 :If (‚éïNULL‚â°avatar)‚à®(0=‚â¢avatar)
     avatar‚Üê''
 :EndIf
 meta‚Üê‚éïJSON(author: author ‚ãÑ created: (‚çï‚éïTS) ‚ãÑ avatar: avatar)
 (‚äÇmeta)‚éïNPUT(dir,'/',name,'.json')1
 ‚çù Install into runtime
 :If 0=##.‚éïNC'UserBots'
     'UserBots'##.‚éïNS''
 :EndIf
 :If 0=##.UserBots.‚éïNC‚äÇauthor
     author ##.UserBots.‚éïNS''
 :EndIf
 ens‚Üê##.UserBots‚çéauthor
 2 ens.‚éïFIX lines
 r‚Üê(name: name ‚ãÑ author: author ‚ãÑ overwritten: overwritten)
